My experience working alongside ChatGPT to generate OpenAPI specs.
As part of a client job (as a newly-minted freelancer!) I got, I needed to design an API. I decided to write an OpenAPI spec. I&rsquo;m so used to gRPC that looking at the OpenAPI JSONs and YAMLs doesn&rsquo;t &ldquo;gel&rdquo; well in my brain, but I do know the basics of API design. And, well&hellip;
With that in mind, and since the project itself revolves around LLMs, I decided to write the spec together with ChatGPT.
